[Oh Min Seong: Why would I wait for you?]
[Taichi: Seriously.]

421
00:29:32,250 --> 00:29:34,920
[Oh Min Seong: Why would I wait for your call?]

422
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:37,140
[Oh Min Seong: You weren't going to call me anyway.]

423
00:29:37,140 --> 00:29:39,100
[Taichi: I thought about it.]
[Oh Min Seong: You thought about it?]

424
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:39,990
[Taichi: Yes.]

425
00:29:40,620 --> 00:29:43,540
[Oh Min Seong: Try it then.]

426
00:29:43,540 --> 00:29:46,130
[Taichi: I'll try next time.]

427
00:29:46,130 --> 00:29:47,470
[Taichi: I thought about it yesterday.]

428
00:29:47,470 --> 00:29:49,340
[Taichi: But you told me not to call you.]

429
00:29:49,870 --> 00:29:51,740
[Oh Min Seong: You liar. You didn't think about it at all.]

430
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:54,240
[Taichi: I did.]
[Oh Min Seong: You didn't want to call me in the first place.]

431
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,210
[Taichi: I did.]

432
00:29:55,470 --> 00:29:58,140
[Taichi: But I really thought about it.]
[Oh Min Seong: Hmm?]

433
00:29:58,140 --> 00:30:00,940
[Taichi: I thought about it.]
[Oh Min Seong: Really?]

434
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:02,030
[Oh Min Seong: Why?]

435
00:30:03,630 --> 00:30:06,500
[Taichi: It's a secret.]
[Oh Min Seong: You want to express your feelings to me?]

436
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,630
[Taichi: This is also a secret.]

437
00:30:10,840 --> 00:30:12,900
[Taichi: 'Cause you kept telling me not to call you.]

438
00:30:13,510 --> 00:30:16,440
[Oh Min Seong: I was just kidding.]

439
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:36,460
[How was Kim Su Min's day?
Please go to the Phone Room to let the other person know your feelings.]

440
00:30:52,180 --> 00:30:56,220
[The person who Su Min—the person
who got Han Gyeol's call—is calling is?]

441
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:58,060
You got a call.

442
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,490
[Kim Sun Wook: Hello?]

443
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:10,170
[Kim Su Min: I'm happy to see you happy.]

444
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:14,170
[Kim Sun Wook: Thank you.]

445
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:17,370
[Kim Su Min: I hope you can be happy tomorrow too.]

446
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:24,050
[Kim Sun Wook: Thank you. I also hope you can be happy every day.]

447
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:29,920
[Kim Su Min: See you later.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Got it. Okay.]

448
00:31:32,860 --> 00:31:37,660
[Su Min's determined heart]

449
00:31:39,530 --> 00:31:42,460
[Kim Su Min: It's really nice.]

450
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:45,130
[Kim Su Min: Sun Wook is still my first choice.]

451
00:31:45,130 --> 00:31:51,540
[Kim Su Min: I hope the last date would be the two of us.]

452
00:31:55,420 --> 00:31:57,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Su Min.]

453
00:31:57,260 --> 00:32:00,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You didn't say see you later.]

454
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:03,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So many "thank yous," it should be Su Min.]

455
00:32:06,870 --> 00:32:10,070
[Kim Sun Wook: Why can all of you see through me?]

456
00:32:11,140 --> 00:32:13,270
[Kim Sun Wook: Although it's a variety show,]

457
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:16,740
[Kim Sun Wook: rather than having to be in a relationship,]

458
00:32:16,740 --> 00:32:20,210
[Kim Sun Wook: I also want to meet a group of good people.]

459
00:32:20,210 --> 00:32:23,150
[Kim Sun Wook: But I don't quite have the thought]

460
00:32:23,150 --> 00:32:24,480
[Kim Sun Wook: of wanting to meet nice people now—]

461
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:27,150
[Kim Sun Wook: I only care about]

462
00:32:27,150 --> 00:32:31,160
[Kim Sun Wook: the person I like.]

463
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:39,170
[How was Cho Yun Jae's day?
Please go to the Phone Room to let the other person know your feelings.]

464
00:32:37,340 --> 00:32:38,780
It seems to be over.

465
00:32:56,780 --> 00:33:01,050
[Has Yun Jae's heart not changed at all?]

466
00:33:07,290 --> 00:33:08,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: Hello?]

467
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:11,030
[Cho Yun Jae: Hello.]

468
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:13,700
[Cho Yun Jae: I had a great date today.]

469
00:33:13,700 --> 00:33:17,700
[Cho Yun Jae: If you're free later,
do you want to go to the convenience store together?]

470
00:33:18,500 --> 00:33:20,640
[Lee Hyun Jun: Sure, let's go.]

471
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:27,310
[Cho Yun Jae: Okay. Bye.]

472
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:31,580
[Lee Hyun Jun: See you later.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Mmhmm.]

473
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:48,930
[Cho Yun Jae: After the day and night date,]

474
00:33:48,930 --> 00:33:52,400
[Cho Yun Jae: I struggled with who I should call.]

475
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:57,740
[Cho Yun Jae: I called Hyun Jun, the person I first picked,]

476
00:33:57,740 --> 00:34:02,280
[Cho Yun Jae: as an attempt to try one last time.]

477
00:34:02,280 --> 00:34:07,620
[Cho Yun Jae: I thought let's talk a little more,
so I plucked up the courage to call him.]

478
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:20,699
[Lee Hyun Jun: Since today is our first date,]

479
00:34:20,699 --> 00:34:23,370
[Lee Hyun Jun: I did think he might not call me.]

480
00:34:23,370 --> 00:34:28,710
[Lee Hyun Jun: Rather than saying I felt burdened,
I felt more sorry.]

481
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:33,510
[Did you hear someone's sincerity?
The call time is over.]

482
00:34:34,050 --> 00:34:38,320
[Taichi hasn't received a call in two days]

483
00:34:38,850 --> 00:34:40,190
[Taichi: I didn't get a call.]

484
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:42,050
[Taichi: But I knew it too.]

485
00:34:42,050 --> 00:34:43,920
[Taichi: While he said he might call me,]

486
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:46,590
[Taichi: he told me a lot about Hyun Jun.]

487
00:34:46,590 --> 00:34:48,460
[Taichi: I guess he really likes Hyun Jun.]

488
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:50,330
[Taichi: That's what I felt.]

489
00:34:50,330 --> 00:34:51,929
[Taichi: Instead of waiting for his call,]

490
00:34:51,929 --> 00:34:54,070
[Taichi: I just want Yun Jae to be honest]

491
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:55,670
[Taichi: and be straightforward towards Hyun Jun—]

492
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:58,070
[Taichi: I wanted that more.]

493
00:35:00,470 --> 00:35:03,410
[There's another man who didn't get a call]

494
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:13,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Honestly, I felt quite frustrated.]

495
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:15,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He said during the night date that]

496
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:16,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: there's more than one person he's interested in,]

497
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:18,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so he must've called the other person.]

498
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:19,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think it's Su Min.]

499
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:22,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Actually, I talked a lot with Su Min.]

500
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:25,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Han Gyeol was just focused on eating.]

501
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:27,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I didn't see them having any communication.]

502
00:35:27,700 --> 00:35:30,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It just felt very sudden.]

503
00:35:30,640 --> 00:35:32,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I felt even worse.]

504
00:35:35,980 --> 00:35:39,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: Is Hyeok Jin asleep?]

505
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:41,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What's wrong?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Nope.]

506
00:35:42,650 --> 00:35:46,390
[Kim Han Gyeol: Do you want to talk?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Oh.]

507
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:54,130
[A heavy atmosphere...]

508
00:35:54,130 --> 00:35:57,060
[Kim Su Min: Scary.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who is scary?]

509
00:35:57,060 --> 00:36:00,000
[Kim Su Min: It felt so tense.]
[Oh Min Seong: Why?]

510
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,070
[Kim Su Min: Older Hyeok Jin.]

511
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:04,270
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Looks like he's a little sad 'cause of Han Gyeol.]

512
00:36:04,770 --> 00:36:08,010
[Han Gyeol mustered up the courage to talk
to Hyeok Jin instead of running away]

513
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:16,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What I thought was what excuse will he come up with?]

514
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:19,750
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hyung, I...]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Mm.]

515
00:36:19,750 --> 00:36:21,890
[Kim Han Gyeol: After today's date, I think]

516
00:36:21,890 --> 00:36:25,090
[Kim Han Gyeol: maybe what I feel isn't liking you.]

517
00:36:28,030 --> 00:36:29,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: But this is not something]

518
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:37,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: I should keep to myself to the very end.]

519
00:36:37,370 --> 00:36:42,710
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I'm here to say it.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You did the right thing.]

520
00:36:42,710 --> 00:36:45,910
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I know.]

521
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:47,510
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can tell.]

522
00:36:47,650 --> 00:36:50,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: You know that]

523
00:36:50,580 --> 00:36:52,220
[Kim Han Gyeol: you're a hyung I really like, right?]

524
00:36:54,190 --> 00:36:56,860
[Kim Han Gyeol: Anyway, liking someone and wanting to get close with someone]

525
00:36:56,860 --> 00:37:00,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: are two different things.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yes.]

526
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:02,190
[Kim Han Gyeol: I should be the latter.]

527
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:05,930
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can tell from the look in your eyes.]

528
00:37:05,930 --> 00:37:10,470
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm also kinda older.]

529
00:37:10,470 --> 00:37:15,010
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Even if it's not people I've dated,
I've met a lot of people.]

530
00:37:15,010 --> 00:37:19,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Most of them look at me
the same way you do.]

531
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:22,750
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

532
00:37:22,750 --> 00:37:24,350
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can see it.]

533
00:37:24,350 --> 00:37:30,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: But I don't mean I hate you, you know?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah. You don't have to explain that.]

534
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:35,830
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's just that what I was worried about
has happened again.]

535
00:37:35,830 --> 00:37:38,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You don't have to feel bad.]

536
00:37:38,230 --> 00:37:40,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I told you last time.]

537
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:42,500
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Whatever choice you make,
I will respect it.]

538
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:46,510
[Kim Han Gyeol: You're so nice to me.]

539
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:49,170
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I got quite confused about what I felt.]

540
00:37:49,170 --> 00:37:53,710
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I understand. We're in this environment after all.]

541
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:58,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I know I've always been like this.]

542
00:37:58,250 --> 00:38:01,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: This is something I should digest.]

543
00:38:02,250 --> 00:38:05,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But whenever something like this happens, I still suffer.]

544
00:38:07,060 --> 00:38:11,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: But I hope you don't.]

545
00:38:21,210 --> 00:38:26,010
[Kim Han Gyeol: If I am hurting you now,]

546
00:38:26,010 --> 00:38:30,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm really sorry.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Don't say sorry.]

547
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:38,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm just pinning it on myself.]

548
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:40,690
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You don't have to say sorry.]

549
00:38:42,560 --> 00:38:46,830
[Eum Hyeok Jin: While I already knew, hearing you say it makes me feel worse.]

550
00:38:50,570 --> 00:38:59,110
[Kim Han Gyeol: But you're still someone super cool to me, you know?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What's the use of being cool?]

551
00:38:59,110 --> 00:39:01,510
[Kim Han Gyeol: Don't say that.]

552
00:39:01,510 --> 00:39:04,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: Doesn't it mean more than just liking you? Saying that you're cool?]

553
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:09,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's because you don't know my skepticism.]

554
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:14,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's too...]

555
00:39:14,180 --> 00:39:16,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I've been through way too many
one-sided relationships.]

556
00:39:16,460 --> 00:39:18,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm used to it.]

557
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:22,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: And because of that I've made the other party feel burdened.]

558
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:26,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The other party would already know
what kind of person I am and what I do,]

559
00:39:26,070 --> 00:39:30,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but I know nothing about them,
so I want to find out more.]

560
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:33,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'll take the initiative to approach and ask.]

561
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:37,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But once that happens, they say it's stressful.]

562
00:39:37,820 --> 00:39:41,550
[Eum Hyeok Jin: This keeps repeating.]

563
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:46,630
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But what can I do?]

564
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:48,490
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The reason they rejected me is all the same.]

565
00:39:48,490 --> 00:39:50,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's a reason that bothered me a lot too.]

566
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:53,830
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But honestly, rejecting me for this
is a big problem for me.]

567
00:39:53,830 --> 00:39:57,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The fact that it's exactly the same here]

568
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: makes it difficult for me to handle it.]

569
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:02,370
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So unknowingly, I cried.]

570
00:40:02,370 --> 00:40:05,840
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was really sad.]

571
00:40:06,910 --> 00:40:10,120
[Can Hyeok Jin's wound heal?]

572
00:40:13,050 --> 00:40:17,860
[Yun Jae goes to Block B]

573
00:40:26,130 --> 00:40:30,400
[Cho Yun Jae: Hyun Jun, if we're going to the convenience store,
you can come out now.]

574
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:32,270
[Lee Hyun Jun: I heard the convenience store]

575
00:40:32,270 --> 00:40:33,940
[Lee Hyun Jun: is only three minutes away.]

576
00:40:34,540 --> 00:40:37,260
[Stare]

577
00:40:43,060 --> 00:40:49,820
[Hyun Jun and Yun Jae decided to talk
instead of going to the convenience store]

578
00:40:47,660 --> 00:40:49,300
But it's quite cold here.

579
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:51,460
There's an air conditioner here.

580
00:40:51,460 --> 00:40:52,590
Is it on heater mode?

581
00:40:58,160 --> 00:41:02,170
[Cho Yun Jae: In my opinion, I can feel he's closer to Sun Wook.]

582
00:41:02,170 --> 00:41:07,510
[Cho Yun Jae: I just want a clear answer on who he's leaning towards.]

583
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:10,440
[Cho Yun Jae: He said it before that he's interested in me.]

584
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:12,840
[Cho Yun Jae: In order to clear my mind,]

585
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:16,320
[Cho Yun Jae: I decided to talk to him in the courtyard.]

586
00:41:16,850 --> 00:41:20,050
[Lee Hyun Jun: We have to talk sooner or later.]

587
00:41:20,050 --> 00:41:24,060
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a situation that'd happen anyway,
so I just took it as it is.]

588
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:28,330
[To put an end to it,
the two men start talking]

589
00:41:30,730 --> 00:41:33,400
[Cho Yun Jae: How was your date today?]

590
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:37,940
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was fun.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Just fun?]

591
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:42,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: Of course.]

592
00:41:42,210 --> 00:41:44,880
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was fun.]

593
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:46,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was fun. What about you?]

594
00:41:47,010 --> 00:41:51,280
[Cho Yun Jae: It's our first date after all, so it was nice.]

595
00:41:54,220 --> 00:42:01,160
[Cho Yun Jae: I guess the empty space in your heart
is more or less settled now?]

596
00:42:01,690 --> 00:42:04,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: Now?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

597
00:42:10,500 --> 00:42:12,900
[Lee Hyun Jun: Now...]

598
00:42:17,180 --> 00:42:20,910
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think I'm totally leaning towards Sun Wook's side.]

599
00:42:21,450 --> 00:42:24,380
[Cho Yun Jae: Is there a special reason?]

600
00:42:30,260 --> 00:42:34,530
[Lee Hyun Jun: There's no special reason.
It's just being attracted.]

601
00:42:39,330 --> 00:42:43,870
[Cho Yun Jae: Completely?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

602
00:42:43,870 --> 00:42:44,940
[Cho Yun Jae: Ah...]

603
00:42:46,270 --> 00:42:49,470
[Cho Yun Jae: Completely, completely?]

604
00:42:51,610 --> 00:42:54,280
[Lee Hyun Jun: Seems like it.]

605
00:43:03,890 --> 00:43:16,440
[Cho Yun Jae: Then why did you go on a date with me?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I was curious about you.]

606
00:43:17,240 --> 00:43:24,980
[Cho Yun Jae: So, how am I?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I know you're a good person.]

607
00:43:29,780 --> 00:43:32,720
[Cho Yun Jae: Is that all?]

608
00:43:37,260 --> 00:43:40,460
[Cho Yun Jae: That I'm a good person...]

609
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:52,740
[Cho Yun Jae: I almost expected that.
So I wasn't that sad.]

610
00:43:52,740 --> 00:43:59,140
[Cho Yun Jae: I wish time could turn back.]

611
00:44:01,550 --> 00:44:06,080
[Cho Yun Jae: To be honest, I want to talk to you more.]

612
00:44:06,080 --> 00:44:11,690
[Cho Yun Jae: But I don't think I can talk to you more comfortably.]

613
00:44:15,160 --> 00:44:21,570
[Cho Yun Jae: But...]

614
00:44:21,570 --> 00:44:31,710
[Cho Yun Jae: I sometimes feel that it's my fault.]

615
00:44:34,910 --> 00:44:39,720
[Cho Yun Jae: I have to take the initiative to come here.]

616
00:44:42,650 --> 00:44:48,790
[Cho Yun Jae: It's not that I don't want to do it subjectively.]

617
00:44:48,790 --> 00:44:51,200
[Cho Yun Jae: It's so hard.]

618
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:59,200
[Cho Yun Jae: I didn't expect this place to be so competitive.]

619
00:44:59,740 --> 00:45:03,210
[Cho Yun Jae: While everyone is working hard,]

620
00:45:03,210 --> 00:45:08,280
[Cho Yun Jae: I stayed in the same room with him. But what was I doing?]

621
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:13,080
[Cho Yun Jae: I also realized my introverted personality.]

622
00:45:13,080 --> 00:45:16,560
[Cho Yun Jae: I feel like I messed up something.]

623
00:45:16,560 --> 00:45:21,360
[Cho Yun Jae: I was very angry at myself.]

624
00:45:22,960 --> 00:45:29,370
[Cho Yun Jae: No matter what I do, you won't change your mind?]

625
00:45:34,710 --> 00:45:38,710
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yes, seems like it.]

626
00:45:43,250 --> 00:45:46,180
[Cho Yun Jae: What a pity.]

627
00:45:52,590 --> 00:45:55,340
[Cho Yun Jae: Do you have anything else to say to me?]

628
00:45:55,340 --> 00:46:00,100
[Cho Yun Jae: Or something you want to say? At the very end.]

629
00:46:01,780 --> 00:46:04,710
[Lee Hyun Jun: Sorry.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Why are you sorry?]

630
00:46:04,710 --> 00:46:18,590
[Lee Hyun Jun: Of course I am. 'Cause I've been giving you chances?]

631
00:46:05,700 --> 00:46:06,700
Why?

